item.title: Grace's Wings Chapter 1 - Page 4
item.description: While drawing Steve's house I looked at a lot of suburban houses and they're all grey, beige, and white. Really boring. So for the interior I made it extra colorful.

item.description: I'm half expecting theories that the lawn flamingo is responsible for all this. Look at it. All smug and pink.

item.title: Grace's Wings Chapter 1 - Page 2
item.description: I really hope you get the mug reference. If you don't just google Big Hug Mug and you'll find the TV Shows it showed up in. One of which I may have slightly disturbed Dan with. ;)

item.title: Grace's Wings Chapter 1 - Page 1
item.description: Everytime I look at Nadia's car I remember how terrible it is. Its the worst model of soviet cars Dan could find and I based the color off of my own family's car which is as old as Nadia's probably is.

item.title: Grace's Wings Chapter 1 - Cover
item.description: When I was making this originally I looked a lot of retro horror movie posters. The ones that were painted rather than photographed. There's a lot of the same color schemes and the composition of them are all very similar so I had a lot of fun imitating their style!
